@hey-nicolasklein 
As a workaround you can simply add `# type: ignore`

like this:
```
uploaded_file = self.client.files.upload(
    file={
      "file_name": "hello.pdf",
      "content": open(file_path, "rb"),
    },
    purpose="ocr",  # type: ignore
)
```

It works fine, just awkward.

