Hi thanks for opening this PR
This issues is on our side and specific to `"tool_choice": "required",` with `mistral-small-latest` (and smaller models)
We were able to reproduce it with the following payload:
```
{
    "model": "mistral-small-latest",
    "messages": [
        {
            "content": "what is the capital of the uk",
            "role": "user"
        }
    ],
    "temperature": 0.0,
    "top_p": 1.0,
    "stream": false,
    "tools": [
        {
            "function": {
                "name": "final_result",
                "parameters": {
                    "properties": {
                        "city": {
                            "title": "City",
                            "type": "string"
                        }
                    },
                    "required": [
                        "city"
                    ],
                    "title": "MyModel",
                    "type": "object"
                },
                "description": "The final response which ends this conversation"
            },
            "type": "function"
        }
    ],
    "tool_choice": "required",
    "n": 1
}
```
We are investigating the root cause and will update you as soon as this is fixed.
